            <title>[DERBY-1752] Fix javadoc to account for changes required by new licence header policy.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-1752</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The published javadoc creates a copyright with the old copyright statement, should be replaced with the collected works copyright,.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
